And the 27-year-old flew to London with the rest of the squad last night ahead of the game at Upton Park.

Advocaat has worked with Johnson at the Academy of Light this week and he took part in a full-scale practice match on Thursday.

When asked during his unveiling press conference if Johnson would play at West Ham, Advocaat said: ‘Everyone who is training is available for selection.’ 

