Advocaat has inherited a side one point and one place above the drop zone. The Dutchman, however, has never been relegated in his 27-year managerial career and does not intend to add demotion to his CV at Sunderland.

‘I have never been relegated and always have the feeling that I will never go down,’ he said. ‘So I don’t really want to talk about relegation.’

 

